<s> I wish to manage XML documents using the w3c DOM standard interface.  </s>
<s> I supposed I could find in this interface a method enabling to format the XML tree content to a string value.  </s>
<s> This support seems to exist, but I found it in the DocumentEx implementation offered in the projectX package com.sun.xml, which is not standard w3c recommendation.  </s>
